OperationalCostManagementTest
├── when accrueAgentCost is called on a fresh decision and leg
│   ├── it should increase costOf agentCostSomi by the amount
│   ├── it should increase cummCostSomi by the amount
│   └── it should emit AgentCostAccrued
├── when accrueAgentCost is called a second time for the same decision and leg
│   ├── it should leave cummCostSomi unchanged after the second call
│   └── it should leave costOf agentCostSomi unchanged after the second call
├── when accrueAgentCost is called for the same decision but a different leg
│   ├── it should accrue the second leg under the same decision
│   └── it should add both legs into cummCostSomi
├── when accrueDataCost is called on a fresh decision
│   ├── it should increase costOf dataCost by the amount
│   ├── it should increase cummDataCost by the amount
│   └── it should emit DataCostAccrued
├── when accrueDataCost is called a second time for the same decision
│   ├── it should leave cummDataCost unchanged after the second call
│   └── it should leave costOf dataCost unchanged after the second call
├── when totalCost is read for a decision
│   └── it should return the accrued agent SOMI and data cost for that decision
└── when many decisions and legs have been accrued
    ├── it should hold cummCostSomi equal to the sum over decisions of costOf agentCostSomi
    └── it should hold cummDataCost equal to the sum over decisions of costOf dataCost
